This paper discusses the development of a modular ontology design library, which is a resource for creating pattern-based ontologies. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG).
